public class FirmwareManifestListOptions
extends ListOptions
    Options to use when listing firmware manifests.

    Note:

    • Filters:

      The list can be filtered server-side on some of the fields of a firmware manifest.

      The following filters are currently supported:

      Server-side filters
      Field Tag Filters
      not equal to equal to greater than less than like in not in
